{"id":258771,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/10/奇闻录-盛世一景-10-23/","date":"2012-10-24T00:15:11Z","modified":"2012-10-24T00:15:11Z","title":"奇闻录 | 盛世一景 10-23","content":"<p><p>2010年4月19日，青海玉树县赛马场山坡上，近四百位僧侣和百余名家属举行了一场遇难者遗体超度仪式。仪式上的僧侣大多从外地赶来。四月玉树气候多变，仪式现场被狂风卷起的沙尘所笼罩。一名遇难者家属在超度仪式上手攒佛珠行礼。数百名僧侣稳坐风中，岿然不动，共同为地震中逝者的灵魂诵经超度。<span></span></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/uploads/3727217_980x1200_0.jpg\"><img src=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/uploads/3727217_980x1200_0.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" /></a></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?a=HxHg5fkcEno:4iywY2zMdIg:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?a=HxHg5fkcEno:4iywY2zMdIg:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?a=HxHg5fkcEno:4iywY2zMdIg:F7zBnMyn0Lo\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?i=HxHg5fkcEno:4iywY2zMdIg:F7zBnMyn0Lo\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?a=HxHg5fkcEno:4iywY2zMdIg:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?i=HxHg5fkcEno:4iywY2zMdIg:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?a=HxHg5fkcEno:4iywY2zMdIg:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" border=\"0\" /></a></div>\n<p><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/qi-wen-lu/~4/HxHg5fkcEno\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\"